{
  "stem": "24814.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And of course, starvation continued to be a problem on the limited rations we could get for them, till we finally got enough food, thank god, and some of them started to get better.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Army rations.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- there was a lot of administrative confusion at first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing they did was to just get C-rations, K, stuff we ate, which was pretty awful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The combat troops.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "C-rations, K-rations, 10-in-1, put them in a big stew pot, mix it up, and feed them out of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, the regulations, they found regulations, well, you can't use army rations, and yadda, yadda, yadda, and they were trying to get the German civilians to bring in food.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could've told them that was a waste of time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they finally had a big captured enemy warehouse in Munich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were able to get food from that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So before I left, the food situation had straightened itself out pretty well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were-- I remember one prisoner, who was not one of the most starved-- we had all degrees, you know-- said, [SPEAKING GERMAN], I had more than enough to eat today.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said I never thought I'd see the day when I'd say I had more than enough to eat, but I had more than enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That felt good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm mentally-- maybe 1,000 in the typhus ward, and they kept coming in every day and dying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would guess somewhere-- it would fluctuate from 500 to 1,000.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Big building.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember these long, long rows of cots.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would guess from 500 to 1,000 most of the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I was never sure of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was some-- some machinery for taking care of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their bodies were taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
